                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-69-off354 t17861213-69-cd355"></join>, forty-eight linen handkerchiefs, value 4 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861213-69-victim593" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Urquhart
                  <interp inst="t17861213-69-victim593" type="surname" value="Urquhart"></interp>
